<dl id="n05037f"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n05" href="#n05037f">N05 (VI.B.2)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n05all.htm#n05037f"> 37(f)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> weekly chapter of faults</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">Nothing daunted, however, the Rev. Brother Thomas Burke betook himself with primitive ardour to his task, and the <mark>&lsquo;chapter of faults&rdquo; weekly</mark>, and sometimes oftener, made all to tremble. <small> William J. Fitz-Patrick, <a name="BURKE" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#BURKE"><cite title="source">The Life of the Very Rev. Thomas N. Burke</cite></a>, (1885) I, 144</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
